        {
            "title": "我要讚佢｜70多歲「垃圾屋」婆婆借宿廣華醫院急症室 社企餐廳接求助清出33車垃圾",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/e16e8ada14ba80fb5c598cb89ff5657b/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250221/_2025022117425149027.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>一名70餘歲獨居婆婆，因入住的老人院住宿期屆滿而被要求離開，但原本居住的單位因多年無人清理變成垃圾屋，一度借宿廣華醫院急症室。直至婆婆被社企餐廳一個「求助牌」吸引，主動向餐廳負責人求助，最終負責人聯同一班無家者充當搬運義工，協助婆婆清出屋內所有垃圾，體積填滿33個660公升垃圾車。義工並協助婆婆重新裝修單位及安置二手傢俱，讓婆婆「重新入伙」返回安樂窩。\n\n</p>\n<p>一直關注無家者及弱勢社群的社企餐廳「Manna‧嗎哪」，土瓜灣分店門口長期放置一招牌，內容寫着「面對困難？同我哋傾下，免費熱飯外，睇下我哋點樣可以陪你行呢段路。」以往不時有無家者或長者主動叩門求助，直至近月有一名年約70餘歲的婆婆上門求助，其訴求一度難倒餐廳負責人。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4094893/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"社企餐廳嗎哪土瓜灣分店門口擺放「求助牌」，鼓勵有需要人士主動求助。(受訪者提供)\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fb13a7bb89751cfe9ff8459db3ae5dfc/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-15_at_11_33_31.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        社企餐廳嗎哪土瓜灣分店門口擺放「求助牌」，鼓勵有需要人士主動求助。(受訪者提供)\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4094894/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"社企餐廳嗎哪關注弱勢社群，聘用更生人士或基層員工外，亦會定期派飯。(受訪者提供)\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9eb64e7c3d164749f7e855492fa39ce5/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-15_at_11_33_32.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        社企餐廳嗎哪關注弱勢社群，聘用更生人士或基層員工外，亦會定期派飯。(受訪者提供)\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4094891/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"70餘歲婆婆(中)家中長年囤積垃圾變垃圾屋，因而向嗎哪負責人求助。(受訪者提供)\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3d4af2ed8f07a27b625d8db2c446122d/2025-02/468184561_989972749838851_3177891121312265303_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        70餘歲婆婆(中)家中長年囤積垃圾變垃圾屋，因而向嗎哪負責人求助。(受訪者提供)\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4094892/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"一班無家者義工上門義務為婆婆清理垃圾。(受訪者提供)\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6c16928fc42630f8cebe3ebce029e743/2025-02/475305433_1035675388601920_3291515235476760750_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        一班無家者義工上門義務為婆婆清理垃圾。(受訪者提供)\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4094895/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"婆婆家中的垃圾總量驚人，合共清出33車660公升垃圾車。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d3aef4390b2f8368c0664acb9f25d844/2025-02/468402876_992048712964588_1713901653478681349_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        婆婆家中的垃圾總量驚人，合共清出33車660公升垃圾車。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>據該名婆婆自述，她原本獨居於一單位內，但因個人缺乏安全感，不斷在外面購買物資或拾荒囤積於屋內，結果雜物越積越多，最終連側身走入家中亦有難度。婆婆指，子女亦因此與她鬧翻，從此不相往來，她其後獲社工轉介入住老人院，但因完約而被請離場。\n\n</p>\n<p>由於原本居住的單位變垃圾屋令婆婆有家歸不得，她又要定期到廣華醫院覆診，索性直接在廣華醫院急症室櫈上借宿數日。由於天氣寒冷，婆婆老弱身體捱不住，她剛好步行至土瓜灣探望朋友期間看到「Manna‧嗎哪」土瓜灣分店的「求助牌」，遂主動叩門向職員求助。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4095000/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"垃圾屋未清理之前，垃圾堆積如山，義工要花3至4天才完全清理。(受訪者提供)\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1df08886d9360f091598593f1bf2dadc/2025-02/468617528_992051479630978_6391230148352748371_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        垃圾屋未清理之前，垃圾堆積如山，義工要花3至4天才完全清理。(受訪者提供)\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4095002/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"清理完垃圾後，屋內單位仍然有異味，牆身及地板骯髒不堪。(受訪者提供)\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/15bdfd75c65c4a3aeae5707429c6a3b4/2025-02/475118250_1035675398601919_4022294692017839027_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        清理完垃圾後，屋內單位仍然有異味，牆身及地板骯髒不堪。(受訪者提供)\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4094999/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"清理完畢後，婆婆家中家窮四壁，而且破爛處極多，需要進行修補。(受訪者提供)\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7d2a412f3d5b7147d8845e2187f77e3b/2025-02/02_26.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        清理完畢後，婆婆家中家窮四壁，而且破爛處極多，需要進行修補。(受訪者提供)\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4094998/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"義工清理完後進行簡單裝修，包括髹油及重鋪地板。(受訪者提供)\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/19ea4b505dc6623e33bf8f2f44659b00/2025-02/01_2__0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        義工清理完後進行簡單裝修，包括髹油及重鋪地板。(受訪者提供)\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4095001/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"義工簡易裝修婆婆的家居，再搬入善心人士捐贈的二手傢俱，讓婆婆「重新入伙」。(受訪者提供)\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/18dd169a44bbaf5d4319bbf4de21040a/2025-02/474924957_1035675315268594_1748015524754360419_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        義工簡易裝修婆婆的家居，再搬入善心人士捐贈的二手傢俱，讓婆婆「重新入伙」。(受訪者提供)\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>嗎哪負責人Leo收到婆婆求助後，曾抵達其單位視察，發現屋內雜物堆積如山，部分高至觸碰天花板，單憑一己之力難以處理。Leo於是聯絡一批嗎哪代為安頓住處的無家者，連同他6個人，花了3至4天才完全搬走屋內垃圾。婆婆期間獲安排入住臨時宿舍，之後他們再為單位進行簡單清潔和裝修，包括拭擦牆面、牆身髹油、重鋪膠地板以及安置二手傢俬入屋後，讓婆婆「重新入伙」。\n\n</p><blockquote>\n<h4>「用時間走入佢生命所有嘅野， 照顧佢呢段時間， 處理佢間屋，之後陪佢去醫院飲茶行街食飯睇戲，你仔女唔照顧你， 咁就我地照顧你。」嗎哪餐廳負責人Leo道。</h4>\n</blockquote>\n<p>負責人Leo稱知道婆婆空虛寂寞感會令她有機會再度拾荒，唯一可以幫助她方法是﹕「陪佢陪到唔再空虛，陪到佢知道唔再係得自己一個人。」Leo希望改變婆婆的習慣之餘，亦呼籲子女更多理解長者長年拾荒背後的原因，嘗試溝通及適時求助，才能改變現狀。\n\n</p>\n<p>--------------------------\n\n</p>\n<p><iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"145\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://e.infogram.com/6cf3e258-8287-4856-845e-5354f235570e?src=embed\" title=\"區區有申訴BANNER\" width=\"100%\"></iframe>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2054151/即時-港聞-我要讚佢-70多歲-垃圾屋-婆婆借宿廣華醫院急症室-社企餐廳接求助清出33車垃圾",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-01 08:06:05",
