        },
        {
            "title": "見義勇為｜輪椅老翁過馬路遭大貨車推行　鐵騎男狂追數百米救人｜有片",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/686e386/0x0/100/none/a6af46d967105bf21b1c86e4b543d6c3/2025-02/New_Project_5__1.jpg\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/50eeb233f5a871efa24436a5e8aa0102/7abbcab30c8d41e193b4e9e5cf10d260-bc342ae5f6ec4ab10fe186c9d901abe8-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67c247eece0d2\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67c247eece0d3\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/7160514940be73b7de41314ba0dcf9e2/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250228/_2025022819174738117.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>在江蘇常州，一名老翁坐著輪椅闖進車流，進入一輛大貨車的視野盲區。隨後，貨車推著輪椅上的老人前行數百米，場面驚險。此時，一名騎電單車路過的黃衣小哥發現異常，果斷掉頭追趕，一路不斷鳴笛提醒，最終叫停大貨車，將老人成功救下，獲評見義勇為。\n\n</p><h2>大貨車視野盲區</h2>\n<p>據央視新聞，該驚險事件發生在本月20日上午10時許，常州經開區橫山橋鎮戚月線新董路口。一名乘坐電動輪椅的8旬老翁違規過馬路，直接鑽入車龍當中，想從大貨車中間的縫隙過去，剛巧前方路口亮起綠燈，車龍啟動前行，因為老翁進入大貨車前方的視線盲區，被緩步啟動的大貨車連同輪椅一路向前推行。\n\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3425773/%E8%A6%8B%E7%BE%A9%E5%8B%87%E7%82%BA%E6%B9%96%E5%8C%97%E4%B8%80%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E5%A2%AE%E6%B1%9F-%E5%8B%87%E7%94%B7%E9%A8%8E%E7%99%BD%E9%BE%8D%E9%A6%AC%E8%90%BD%E6%B0%B4%E7%87%9F%E6%95%91%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87\">見義勇為｜湖北一男子墮江 勇男騎「白龍馬」落水營救｜有片</a></strong>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"電動輪椅老翁亂過馬路，想由車龍中橫過。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c0ec1f7e2011413c0155ee42cf599595/2025-02/vlcsnap-2025-02-28-15h24m47s620.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        電動輪椅老翁亂過馬路，想由車龍中橫過。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"老翁進入大貨車的盲眼區。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b9b6ced8b45f64851eb8c4d2423ee198/2025-02/vlcsnap-2025-02-28-15h24m52s627.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        老翁進入大貨車的盲眼區。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"老人在輪椅上被大貨車推行數百米。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9a79596ffec46eb4806c73e3340034bf/2025-02/vlcsnap-2025-02-28-15h24m56s903.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        老人在輪椅上被大貨車推行數百米。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"鐵騎男發現了老翁被頂行。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9848ff4ba86ae4927d2e1c6ace71ee8c/2025-02/vlcsnap-2025-02-28-15h25m06s707.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鐵騎男發現了老翁被頂行。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"鐵騎男調頭狂追救人。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a88869370c2e93570ea1731e7867ff7c/2025-02/vlcsnap-2025-02-28-15h25m25s481.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鐵騎男調頭狂追救人。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"老人在輪椅上被大貨車推行數百米，非常驚險。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/eb520bd7f60b891f56321ba370a6e9ac/2025-02/vlcsnap-2025-02-28-15h25m35s250.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        老人在輪椅上被大貨車推行數百米，非常驚險。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"鐵騎男調頭狂追，猛按喇叭示警，終成功救人。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0824f4eb1de4f6c5ebd729b51242d3ae/2025-02/vlcsnap-2025-02-28-15h25m47s031.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鐵騎男調頭狂追，猛按喇叭示警，終成功救人。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"網民激讚鐵騎男。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9141414f866e8bdb1f968b2c75117b96/2025-02/Clipboard49_14.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        網民激讚鐵騎男。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"網民激讚鐵騎男。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4127d868b5c8c208d5db58de4c513518/2025-02/Clipboard50_12.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        網民激讚鐵騎男。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"網民激讚鐵騎男。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fd830146cfc7933248c3f39cab7cc218/2025-02/Clipboard51_14.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        網民激讚鐵騎男。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"網民激讚鐵騎男。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/aec26b5c7b4e126584b167e90e1f838e/2025-02/Clipboard52_13.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        網民激讚鐵騎男。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3424732/%E8%A6%8B%E7%BE%A9%E5%8B%87%E7%82%BA%E6%B5%B7%E5%8D%97%E5%B0%8F%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%A9%E8%A2%AB%E5%B7%A8%E6%B5%AA%E6%8D%B2%E8%B5%B0-%E9%95%B7%E9%AB%AE%E5%93%A5%E7%84%A1%E6%87%BC%E8%A2%AB%E6%B2%96%E8%B5%B0%E6%8B%BF%E5%91%BD%E6%95%91%E4%BA%BA%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87\">見義勇為｜海南小女孩被巨浪捲走 長髮哥無懼被沖走拿命救人｜有片</a></strong>\n</p>\n<p>貨車司機未有絲毫察覺，千鈞一髮之際。一位騎電單車的黃衣小哥從對面駛至，他發現後立即調頭追趕貨車，追了數百米，猛按喇叭示警，司機注意到喊叫提醒後，趕緊停車，這才發現自己的車頭頂了位大爺，趕緊報警。警方到場時，黃衣男已經離開。\n\n</p>\n<p>警方說，若不是好心路人及時出手，後果不堪設想，於是發布尋人訊息，要尋找這名熱心小哥。26日下午，經開區見義勇為基金會負責人為該名「黃衣小哥」袁建龍送上見義勇為表彰和獎勵。\n\n</p>\n<p>袁建龍謙虛表示，自己只是做了順手而為的事，「腦子裡想到的就是趕緊要去把車攔下來，太危險了！」\n\n</p>\n<p>警方也提醒長輩，出門要遵守交通法規，多一分關心，少一點危險。\n\n</p>\n<p><strong>不少網友也在評論區為小哥點讚：</strong>\n</p>\n<p>「看似救了老人，實則救了司機」；<br/>\n「不要責怪外賣員送晚了，也許他正在救人」；<br/>\n「黃衣小哥叫一生平安，他的妻子叫幸福美滿，一家人都健康平安」；<br/>\n「很奇怪的事情，中國人就是素不相識，但又好像心連著心！」；<br/>\n「救了兩個家庭」。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2055521/即時-中國-見義勇為-輪椅老翁過馬路遭大貨車推行-鐵騎男狂追數百米救人-有片",
