            "title": "英足盃│守護神歸位擒「狼」 博般茅贏2:1/3:1",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\" 般尼茅夫正選中堅沙巴爾今晚可以上陣。Reuters\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/11d78ecc988711eb9dc6fc9a47ca375d/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250228/_2025022821205671511.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"> 般尼茅夫正選中堅沙巴爾今晚可以上陣。Reuters</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p></p><h3>足智彩球賽編號：FB8276<br/>\n般尼茅夫 VS 狼隊<br/>\nNow651台今晚11:00直播<br/>\n推介：般尼茅夫波膽2:1/3:1</h3>\n<p>般尼茅夫前仗英超負於狼隊腳下，皆因正選中堅沙巴爾在30分鐘領紅牌出場，被罰在聯賽停賽3場，反而今場足總盃可以上陣為球隊復仇，櫻桃今場有望以主力出戰，勝望稍高半線。趁狼隊近期入球能力有改善，連續5場取得入球，一於博主隊以波膽2:1/3:1贏波出線。馬高\n\n</p>\n<p>英足盃戰火蔓延，YouTube頻道《猜波台》主持人出盡法寶，同大家實時講波，一齊分享大賽氣氛。想了解最新資訊，請立即進入《猜波台》頻道：<br/>\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzbQyqpgmd99vcNs3AaMK7A\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzbQyqpgmd99vcNs3AaMK7A</a>\n</p><div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -12px; top: 289.844px;\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\"> </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
