        {
            "title": "西甲│弱方主場讓平半 信鬼盤照捧基羅納",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"切爾達（藍衫）近期賽績和表現皆極弱。Reuters\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/3f91e559eddced79c9527ef48bf1ffab/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250228/_2025022821375477233.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">切爾達（藍衫）近期賽績和表現皆極弱。Reuters</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p></p><h3>足智彩球賽編號：FB8262<br/>\n基羅納 VS 切爾達<br/>\nNow632台今晚9:00直播<br/>\n推介: 主客和主勝</h3>\n<p>西甲聯賽水準低，近年更出現不少鬼盤和令人「意外」的賽果，基羅納近8場1勝7負，賽績和表現皆極弱，今晚在主場面對近3戰取得2勝1和的切爾達，馬會居然開出主隊讓平手/半球低水的盤口，擺到明請君入甕，客隊不宜沾手，信鬼盤應直取主客和主勝，若即場客隊領先，必加注主隊反勝。\n\n</p><div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -91px; top: -12px;\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\"> </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
