        {
            "title": "天文台｜早晚有一兩陣微雨  最高氣溫約25度  吹和緩東至東南風",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/7dccf46530aef1ac6782fe95a6d99c06/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250301/_2025030106400275869.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">蔡楚輝攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>一股潮濕的海洋氣流正影響廣東沿岸。本港方面，今早沿岸有薄霧，橫瀾島的能見度曾下降至1000米左右。\n\n</p>\n<p>本港地區今日大致多雲。早晚有一兩陣微雨及沿岸有薄霧。日間部分時間有陽光及相當溫暖，最高氣溫約25度。吹和緩東至東南風。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4111091/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"本港地區今日早晚有一兩陣微雨及沿岸有薄霧。蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/664c5ccfd9246207366946c15340b6c2/2025-03/40.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        本港地區今日早晚有一兩陣微雨及沿岸有薄霧。蔡楚輝攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4111092/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ddc54a639a0b986b347566f9d66695ef/2025-03/Screenshot_2025-02-28_at_10_34_09_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4111093/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8351fd93577fa8ea7090c53f987ab696/2025-03/Screenshot_2025-02-28_at_10_34_19_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4111094/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"本港地區今日早晚有一兩陣微雨及沿岸有薄霧。蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1e1c19028d21f9f6a5084de62d4a360a/2025-03/41.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        本港地區今日早晚有一兩陣微雨及沿岸有薄霧。蔡楚輝攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4111095/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/213c625491cbf56353e45acb5761f155/2025-03/43.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        蔡楚輝攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>展望星期日及星期一潮濕有霧，日間相當溫暖。星期二漸轉吹東北風及有驟雨。下週中至後期氣溫逐步下降及有幾陣雨，接近週末相當清涼，氣溫下降至14度左右。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
